# Agora Business OS — Environment Configuration

## For Expo (app.json `extra` field)

Add your Supabase credentials to `app.json` under `expo.extra`:

```json
{
  "expo": {
    "extra": {
      "SUPABASE_URL": "https://your-project.supabase.co",
      "SUPABASE_ANON_KEY": "your-anon-key"
    }
  }
}
```

## Or use a `.env` file with `expo-env`

Create `.env` in the project root:

```
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
```

## Offline / Libre Mode

If you leave these blank, the app runs fully offline (Libre mode) with
all data stored locally via AsyncStorage. No Supabase account required.

## AI Advisor

The AI Advisor uses the Anthropic API directly from the app.
Add your API key in app.json:

```json
"extra": {
  "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "sk-ant-..."
}
```

> ⚠️ For production, proxy AI calls through your Supabase Edge Function
> (same as the web version) so the API key is never in the bundle.
